	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />What I am working on is running the board from a USB wall plug, and I want to make sure I am not pushing too much amperage to it. Could anyone with a stick power brick and an ammeter measure it for me? I would prefer to match spec if possible. I have a few plugs to choose from,m and the one that is physically smallest does 5v DC @ 1.0A.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


