	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" /><div class="quotetitle"><b>Quote:</b></div><div class="quotecontent">Deck will be nodded for <strong>Stereo</strong> AV and powered through a USB B type jack.</div><br />The NES can't be in Stereo, ever.<br /><br />All those so-called stereo mods are shit. They either send trebble to one side and bass to the other, or sends Square + noise channels to one side and triangle to the other.<br /><br />The NES console and games were designed to be in mono, and this can't be changed by a mod.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
